<plot>This live-action/animated documentary follows the history of Peter Pan, from his creation by J.M. Barrie to on-stage productions, and finally film, incorporating interviews with actors and actresses of various Peter Pan productions throughout the years. Rupert Grint (Ron Weasley of the Harry Potter films) stars as the voice of Peter Pan and Jane Horrocks ("Little Voice," 1998) supplies the voice of Tinkerbell.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?229521</url></doc>
